#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1636
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Date</guilabel> if you want to specify only a date for the "
#| "alarm: in this case the alarm will be displayed at the first opportunity "
#| "on or after the configured start-of-day time, on the specified date. "
#| "(<link linkend=\"preferences-general\">Configuring &kalarm;</link> "
#| "describes how to set the start-of-day time.)"
msgid ""
"<guilabel>At date/time</guilabel> to enter the date and time when the alarm "
"is to be triggered. Check <guilabel>Any time</guilabel> if you want to "
"specify only a date for the alarm: in this case the alarm will be displayed "
"at the first opportunity on or after the configured start-of-day time, on "
"the specified date. (<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuring &kalarm;"
