"følger:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3024
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Sendmail</guilabel>: When an email alarm is triggered, the "
#| "email is sent automatically using <application>&Sendmail;</application>. "
