"eller et program som virker ligesom <application>&Sendmail;</application> "
"for eksempel <application>postfix</application> eller <application>qmail</"
"application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3036
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Copy sent emails into &kmail;'s sent-items folder</guilabel>: "
