#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-i</option>, <option>--interval <replaceable>period</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-i</option>, <option>--interval <replaceable>periode</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the interval between repetitions of the alarm. Hours/minutes are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, where "
"<replaceable>n</replaceable> is a number, &eg; 3H30M. Other time periods are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nX</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
"replaceable> is a number and <replaceable>X</replaceable> is one of the "
"following letters: Y (years), M (months), W (weeks), D (days). If <option>--"
"recurrence</option> is also specified, Y (years) and M (months) are not "
"allowed. Mandatory if <option>--repeat</option> or <option>--until</option> "
"is specified."
msgstr ""
"Angiv intervallet mellem gentagelser af alarmen. Timer/minutter angives i "
"formatet <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, hvor <replaceable>n</replaceable> "
"er et tal, f.eks. 3H30M. Andre tidsperioder angives i formatet "
"<replaceable>nX</replaceable>, hvor <replaceable>n</replaceable> er et tal "
"og <replaceable>X</replaceable> er et af følgende bogstaver: Y (år), M "
"(måneder), W (uger), D (dage). Hvis <option>--recurrence</option> også er "
"angivet er , Y (år) og M (måneder) ikke tilladt. Krævet hvis <option>--"
"repeat</option> eller <option>--until</option> er angivet."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3472
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-k</option>, <option>--korganizer</option>"
msgstr "<option>-k</option>, <option>--korganizer</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the alarm as an event in &korganizer;'s active calendar."
msgstr "Vis alarmen som en begivenhed i &korganizer;s aktive kalender."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-l</option>, <option>--late-cancel <replaceable>period</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-l</option>, <option>--late-cancel <replaceable>periode</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3479
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Output a reminder alarm the specified length of time before the main "
#| "alarm and each of its recurrences (if any). Hours/minutes are specified "
#| "in the format <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
#| "replaceable> is a number, &eg; 3H30M. Other time periods are specified in "
#| "the format <replaceable>nX</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
#| "replaceable> is a number and <replaceable>X</replaceable> is one of the "
#| "following letters: W (weeks), D (days). This option cannot be specified "
#| "with <option>--exec</option>, <option>--mail</option> or <option>--"
#| "reminder-once</option>."
msgid ""
"Cancel the alarm if it cannot be triggered within the specified "
"<replaceable>period</replaceable> after the correct time. Hours/minutes are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, where "
"<replaceable>n</replaceable> is a number, &eg; 3H30M. Other time periods are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nX</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
"replaceable> is a number and <replaceable>X</replaceable> is one of the "
"following letters: W (weeks), D (days). The default value of "
"<replaceable>period</replaceable> is 1 minute."
msgstr ""
"Vis en påmindelsesalarm det angivne tidsrum inden hovedalarmen og for hver "
"af dens gentagelser (hvis der er nogen). Timer/minutter angives i formatet "
"<replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, hvor <replaceable>n</replaceable> er et "
"tal, f.eks. 3H30M. Andre tidsperioder angives i formatet <replaceable>nX</"
"replaceable>, hvor <replaceable>n</replaceable> er et tal og <replaceable>X</"
"replaceable> er et af følgende bogstaver: Y (år), M (måneder), W (uger), D "
"(dage). Dette flag kan ikke angives sammen med <option>--exec</option>, "
"<option>--mail</option> eller <option>--reminder-once</option>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-L</option>, <option>--login</option>"
msgstr "<option>-L</option>, <option>--login</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
